    java.lang.Comparable<com.android.volley.Request<org.json.JSONObject>>

    public class JsonObjectRequest
extends com.android.volley.toolbox.JsonObjectRequest
    A wrapper class of request for retrieving a JSONObject response body at a given URL, allowing for an optional JSONObject to be passed in as part of the request body.
